name: 费思成
bio_zh: 我目前是西北工业大学自动化学院的四年级（2022年-至今）博士研究生，师从张鼎文教授。我的研究兴趣包括多智能体协同建图 、3D视觉
bio_en: I am currently a fourth-year Ph.D. student (2022–present) in the School of Automation at Northwestern Polytechnical University, advised by Prof. Dingwen Zhang.My research interests include multi-agent collaborative mapping and 3D vision.
research_interests: 多智能体协同建图 、3D视觉
